Packages
FESI.AST Abstract syntaxt tree generated by the javaCC parser generator.
FESI.awtgui Implements the gui interfaces for the AWT.
FESI.Bsf  
FESI.ClassFile Utility routines to generate byte code for the event handler.
FESI.Data Contains all native FESI objects.
FESI.Exceptions Contains the exceptions specific to FESI, but without JSException which is defined in jslib.
FESI.Extensions Contains the standard Extensions.
FESI.gui Defines the interface of the gui functions, so that they can be implemented with AWT and Swing.
FESI.Interpreter Contains the interpreter itself (the xxxVisitor classes), then driver routines (Evaluator), the interactive interpreter (Interpret) and may utility classes.
FESI.jslib Contains the public routines to access FESI objects and functions.
FESI.Parser Parser generated by the javaCC parser generator.
FESI.swinggui Contains the implementation of the gui functions defined in the interfaces of the package gui.
FESI.Tests Contains a few classes used for the validation of FESI.
